>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">·ºàŒΩŒ∏\u003C/supplied>ŒµŒºœåŒ∫œÅŒπœÑŒøœÇ \u003Cg type=\"dipunct\">:\u003C/g> ·ºêœÜŒØŒµœÑŒø ·ºåœÄŒµŒªŒπŒΩ ·ºêŒΩŒ≥œÖŒ¨œÉŒ±œÉŒ∏Œ±Œπ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Cunclear>Œº\u003C/unclear>Œ± Œ¥·Ω≤ ·ºîœÜŒ± Œµ·º¥ŒºŒµŒπŒΩ Œ∫Œ±œÑŒµŒªŒ¨Œ∂ŒµœÑŒø œÑŒøÕÇŒΩ ŒõŒµŒøŒΩœÑŒØŒΩŒøÃÑŒΩ ŒæŒµ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/> ŒúœçœÉŒ∫ŒøÃÑŒΩŒ± \u003Cg type=\"dipunct\">:\u003C/g> ·ºêŒΩ œÑ·æ∂Œπ œÄŒªŒ±œÑŒµŒØŒ±Œπ Œ∏ŒøÃÑŒ∫Œ≠ŒøŒΩœÑŒ±œÇ \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/> ·ºÄœÅŒ≥œçœÅŒπŒøŒΩ ·ºîœáŒøÃÑŒΩ h·øñŒ∫Œµ Œ≤ŒøŒøÕÇŒΩ œÑŒπŒºŒ¨ŒΩ Œø·ΩêŒ∫ ·ºêœÄœÅŒØŒ±œÑŒø\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Cunclear>Œ±Œπ\u003C/unclear> œÄŒøœÑ‚Äô ·ºòŒΩœÄŒµŒ¥ŒøŒ∫ŒªŒµÕÇ œÑ·Ω∏ŒΩ ŒúŒΩŒ±œÉŒπŒºŒ¨œáŒøœÖ œÄŒøœÑŒµÃÑÃÅŒΩŒ∏ŒµœÑŒø\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>\u003ChandShift new=\"#h2\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>Œ≥ŒµŒΩŒ≠œÉŒ∏ŒøÃÑ ·ºêŒΩ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Œ≥\u003C/supplied>œÖŒ¨œÉŒ±œÉŒ∏Œ±Œπ\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Arena 1989 (IGASM I)\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\n                        \u003Cnote>Miller: ŒëœÄŒ≠\u003Cunclear>Œª\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\">Œª\u003C/supplied>\u003Cunclear>Œπ\u003C/unclear>\u003Cdel rend=\"erasure\">ŒΩ\u003C/del>ŒΩ\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cp>[...] Myskon, son of Damis son of Kobetos [...] Anthemokritos bade Apellis offer security \n                    [...] said [...] was; he came upon [...] of the Leontines [...] Myskon sitting along the avenue [...] \n                    came (not?) having the money, the price of the cattle; he did not buy [...] went to Empedokles, \n                    son of Mnasimachos [...] let [...] become (liable?) to act as surety (trans. by Miller).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cp>[...] Myskon, figlio di Damis figlio di Kobetos [...] Anthemokritos ordin√≤ ad Apelis(?) di agire da garante  \n                    [...] disse [...] era; si imbatt√© [...] dei Leontini [...] Myskon seduto lungo il viale [...] \n                    venne (non?) avendo il denaro, il prezzo del bestiame; non compr√≤ [...] and√≤ da Empedokles, \n                    figlio di Mnasimachos [...] lasci√≤ che [...] diventasse garante.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!-- (in progress) The text appears on the obverse of an opisthographic lamina with a defixio on the reverse (ISic030019, Arena II(2), no. 45). -->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGASM1\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Arena\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>77\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VC9IHZAR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Miller\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1973\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>fig. p. 37\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/INAEX86G\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Brugnone\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1980-1981\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>437-438\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/86H6PMPS\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Van Effenterre and Ruz√©\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1995\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>228-230 no.63\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/MMGV74CD\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
